Class NiFormulaicAmountCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.output.nicells.NiOutCell
      • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.output.nicells.NiAmountCell

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable, NumberedCell

    public class NiFormulaicAmountCell
extends NiAmountCell
    a NiAmountCell subclass with some extra possibilities
    • each cell holds a list of named values (see values)
    • holding undefined values, which is one of UNDEFINED, PLUS_INFINITY, MINUS_INFINITY
    • cells are formatted potentially differently (see CellVisitor.visit(NiFormulaicAmountCell, CellColumn))
